{"tid":1991771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嵐成員櫻井翔因發燒暫時未能主持新聞節目《NEWS ZERO》","createTime":"2020-04-27T16:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T16:12:36.000Z","uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"59b6366f8eee69d96c2bbca50ef56d4ad1cb7c84","tid":1991771,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"今晚（4月27日晚）， 嵐的櫻井翔因發燒而沒有上他所主持的新聞節目。他為日本電視台的晚上新聞節目《NEWS ZERO》做男主播。女主播在節目內跟他通電話而問他的情況，他說只發微熱而已，沒有其他病徵，可是為了安全主動在家觀察。<br />\n<a href=\"https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20200427-04270266-sph-ent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadlines.yahoo.co.jp%2Fhl%3Fa%3D20200427-04270266-sph-ent&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4VSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=cd26b455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20200427-04270266-sph-ent</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://johosokuhou.com/2020/04/28/30166/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjohosokuhou.com%2F2020%2F04%2F28%2F30166%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4VSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=f7d4193f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://johosokuhou.com/2020/04/28/30166/</a><br />\nNEWSZERO<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntv.co.jp/zero/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntv.co.jp%2Fzero%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4VSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=c14282b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntv.co.jp/zero/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/poo0Ecg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpoo0Ecg.jpg&h=23ad68b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f985e1b6bef822f7766a6f1046b56ba57d9daf0e","tid":1991771,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"有働由美子アナウンサー（５１）から「体調が大丈夫ということを聞いて安心しました。そういう選択をしてくださってありがとうございます。私たちスタッフに感染を広げないという判断ですよね」と確認されると「視聴者の皆さんに申し訳ないと思っていますが、安全第一と思って」とコメント。この日の放送は自宅から見届けるという。"}]}